{
  "stem": "25809.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The bell rang.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She pulled the cord.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which would open the downstairs front door--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the street--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the street.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And two or three guys came at tremendous speed up the stairway, because I remember the [INAUDIBLE], the sound of the steps, of somebody running with tremendous speed, running up the stairway.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And barging into the room where we were all sitting-- and my father was sitting with his back towards the window.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was standing behind the back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think we were about ready to go and start to-- some movies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my-- my father was standing there, and he sees those guys barging in, and he knew immediately that it was the SS Polizei.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, we are the SS Polizei.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you are Jew Rubens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you are so and so and you are so and so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you are under the equivalent of arrest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We will take you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One of the guys walked immediately into the hiding place, picked up the little cash box with the securities-- took that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then my father was-- he was standing up, and I was standing behind my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he goes from-- he goes over his hip pocket very carefully, very suave-like.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'm standing behind me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had-- he always carried big wads of money on him, because he couldn't go to the bank, right?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he had a lot of money on him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he pulls the money out of it and pushes the money to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like he was going like-- like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm standing there for a moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, what does he want?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He couldn't talk to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] what does he want?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I'm this eight-year-old kid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm not that bright yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
